-- UniCredit Not Considering Exit From Hungary
-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 2010-10-12T15:24:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/unicredit-isn-t-considering-exit-from-hungary-even-after-new-tax-approved.html
UniCredit SpA doesn’t plan to exit
Hungary after the country imposed a special tax on financial
institutions, a spokeswoman said. The bank’s plans for Hungary
haven’t changed, she said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
